<CONTENT id="_3793141_1"><TITLE value="Session 2"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;h6&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46885306_1" alt="" width="570" height="321" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h6&gt;&lt;h5&gt;Overview&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this session we learn to identify the need for cyber security for an organisation.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;We will focuss on the following two matters:&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ul style="list-style-type: disc;"&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Awareness of Cyber Security for organisations&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Definition of Cyber threats&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Student Readings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;News:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.abc.net.au/news/2024-07-20/what-happened-crowdstrike-global-outage-explainer/104122582" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12pt;"&gt;What actually happened inside the CrowdStrike update to cause a worldwide IT breakdown? - ABC News&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;What part of the cyber security CIA triad was challenged by this event?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Cisco CyberSecurity Essentials.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol style="list-style-type: decimal;"&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Active Reading: CISCO: rest of Chapter 1 and&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Active Reading: CISCO: Chapter 2.2 (11 pages)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Active Reading: CISCO: Chapter 2.3 (7 pages)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Active Reading: CISCO: Chapter 2.5.1 (5 pages)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;For your review, pay particular attention to protecting the data belonging to individuals, as well as the data belonging to organisations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Portfolio Tasks&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Attempt PART-ONE of AT1 . When completed submit using the submission item below this item.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;First, Check the information on assessment submission requirements under the Assessments tab.&lt;/p&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
